( '29', '16', 'How do I pay for a custom essay?', 'You must add funds to your account to use our research paper writing service, but rest assured, these funds won\'t be used without your consent.  You\'ll receive your completed assignments via email once your writer finalizes them. Review the paper and request free revisions if needed. If you are satisfied, complete the payment to the writer. This secure and transparent process puts you in control, ensuring the paper meets your expectations.  Place your trust in our specialized and professional service. Each piece is meticulously crafted and customized to align perfectly with your needs and preferences, reinforcing our commitment to excellence.', '2024-04-23 12:59:07', '2024-04-23 12:59:07' ),
( '30', '16', 'How do I pay for a custom essay?', 'You must add funds to your account to use our research paper writing service, but rest assured, these funds won\'t be used without your consent.  You\'ll receive your completed assignments via email once your writer finalizes them. Review the paper and request free revisions if needed. If you are satisfied, complete the payment to the writer. This secure and transparent process puts you in control, ensuring the paper meets your expectations.  Place your trust in our specialized and professional service. Each piece is meticulously crafted and customized to align perfectly with your needs and preferences, reinforcing our commitment to excellence.', '2024-04-23 12:59:07', '2024-04-23 12:59:07' ),
( '31', '16', 'What sets Sop Craft apart from other SOP writing services?', 'Sop Craft stands out through the expertise of its PhD writers, personalized approach to each client, and dedication to delivering standout SOPs and admission essays that mirror the unique qualities and aspirations of applicants.', '2024-04-23 12:59:07', '2024-04-23 12:59:07' ),
( '33', '17', 'Can Sop Craft help with PhD applications?', 'You must add funds to your account to use our research paper writing service, but rest assured, these funds won\'t be used without your consent.  You\'ll receive your completed assignments via email once your writer finalizes them. Review the paper and request free revisions if needed. If you are satisfied, complete the payment to the writer. This secure and transparent process puts you in control, ensuring the paper meets your expectations.  Place your trust in our specialized and professional service. Each piece is meticulously crafted and customized to align perfectly with your needs and preferences, reinforcing our commitment to excellence.', '2024-04-23 13:22:15', '2024-04-23 13:22:15' ),
( '34', '17', 'Can Sop Craft help with PhD applications?', 'Absolutely, Sop Craft provides expert assistance with PhD applications. We offer tailored statement of purpose writing services aimed at impressing admissions committees and securing admission to esteemed doctoral programs.', '2024-04-23 13:22:15', '2024-04-23 13:22:15' ),
( '37', '19', 'Can You Rewrite My Paper?', 'Yes, we can absolutely rewrite your paper and deliver it to you on time. Please give us your requirements through our order form and make the necessary payment to get us started. Upon reviewing your order, our team will assign a suitable writer who can work on rewriting your essay.', '2024-04-24 04:53:32', '2024-04-24 04:53:32' ),
( '38', '19', 'How Fast to Rewrite My Paper?', 'Usually, it depends on the length of the paper. Our writers get started with the rewriting process as soon as they are assigned to your task. However, the whole process of rewriting will depend on numerous parameters, such as the length of the essay, the complexity of the topic, and the deadline. Nonetheless, we promise to deliver it on time.', '2024-04-24 04:53:32', '2024-04-24 04:53:32' ),
( '39', '19', 'Who Will Rewrite My Essay?', 'We have professional writers and editors in our team and they will rewrite the essay. Once you fill out the information on the order form, such as subject, task type, task topic, and academic level, we will assign an appropriate writer. Rest assured, all our writers are experienced and well-qualified for the task.', '2024-04-24 04:53:32', '2024-04-24 04:53:32' ),
( '40', '19', 'Can You Rewrite Essay Texts Confidentially?', 'Yes, we maintain confidentiality and never disclose or share your personal details or essay texts with any other external parties. We are a professional service provider and we prioritize the security and data privacy of our clients. Rest assured, you can submit your personal information and order details without a second thought.', '2024-04-24 04:53:32', '2024-04-24 04:53:32' ),
( '41', '19', 'Can you rewrite my essay for me once again if I don\'t like the first draft?', 'Yes, EduCrafter provides a revision request facility for all the customers to get amendments done. In case, you need changes or your requirements get changed and you want us to rework the same essay, you can place a revision request. Once the request gets processed, the writer will rework it.', '2024-04-24 04:53:32', '2024-04-24 04:53:32' ),
